uk.gov.gchq.palisade.cache.service.request

Class AddCacheRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.service.request.Request
      • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.cache.service.request.AddCacheRequest

  • public class AddCacheRequest
extends Request
    This class is used to request that a DataRequestConfig relating to a unique RequestId, that is set when the client registers there request for data, is added to the cache in the cache service.
